
Stripe Notes
============

Date
    1 Dic 2023


Webhooks

    A type of event listener

    Allow servers to push information to URL's in real time

Testing cards

    https://stripe.com/docs/testing#cards

    There are card numbers you can use there

        Success

            4000004840008001

        Decline
            4000000000000002

        Tokens (aliases)

            tok_visa

            tok_visa_debit

Stripe Cli

    Install
        brew install stripe/stripe-cli/stripe

    Login
        $ stripe login

        $ stripe login --project-name <myProject>
        
    Check configuration

        $ stripe config --list

            [default] === Project name
            account_id = 
            device_name = 'Pablos-MacBook-Pro.local'
            display_name = 'bite-size.mx'
            live_mode_api_key = 'x'
            live_mode_key_expires_at = '2024-03-01'
            live_mode_pub_key = 'x'
            test_mode_api_key = 'x'
            test_mode_key_expires_at = ''
            test_mode_pub_key = ''


    List API commands

        $ stripe resources

            Will show all available commands

        $ stripe open api

            Will open the api documentations


Testing web hooks

    $ stripe listen --forward-to localhost:4242/webhook

    $ stripe trigger checkout.session.completed

